            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日10:19，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲1248.96點（或2.68%），暫報47833.42點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.52%</li><li>近 1 月：-1.93%</li><li>近 3 月：-4.92%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.04%</li><li>今年以來：-3.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)領漲。宣偉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SHW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SHW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SHW-US</a>)上漲6.97%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)上漲6.1%；卡特彼勒(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CAT-US</a>)上漲5.41%；高盛集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GS-US</a>)上漲4.8%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data